data.description: Beautiful Townhome with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, is located in an excellent and established community with a great location, and close to shops, supermarkets, recreation, parks, etc. This unit has a great and preferential location within the community, it has parking for 3 vehicles, 1 covered parking space and 2 outdoor parking spaces, it has an incredible and very nice common green area. The owner's bedroom is large in size and is accompanied by a bathroom, with a shower, bathtub and dressing room. The property has fresh paint internally and a new architectural Roof recently installed. The property is sold as is.  This beautiful property awaits you.
